-- RAM: 0.5 GB × 730 hours × $0.000231 = $0.08/month
-- CPU: 0.5 vCPU × 730 hours × $0.000463 = $0.17/month
-- **Subtotal**: ~$0.25/month
-
-**MySQL Database** (2GB RAM, 1 vCPU, 24/7):
