-
-**Cons**:
-
-- ❌ More complex database management
-- ❌ Higher cost (multiple databases)
-- ❌ More complex migrations
-
-**Cost**: $5 base + ($2-3 per client database) = $5 + $2n where n = number of clients
-
-**Example**: 5 clients = $5 + $10 = $15/month
-
