-**After**:
-
-```typescript
-const form = screen.getByRole("form");
-expect(form).toHaveAttribute("action", "/submit");
-```
-
-**Before**:
-
-```typescript
-await waitFor(() => {
-  expect(screen.getByText("Success")).toBeInTheDocument();
-  expect(screen.getByText("Done")).toBeInTheDocument();
-});
-```
-
-**After**:
-
-```typescript
